  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Subject is age 18 or older and in good health (Investigator discretion) with a recent
             stable medical history

          -  Subject has a diagnosis of rheumatoid arthritis as defined by the 1987-revised ACR
             criteria

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Subject considered by the investigator, for any reason, to be an unsuitable candidate
             for the study

          -  Female subject who is pregnant or breast-feeding or considering becoming pregnant
